ati-Hill\n|28,671\n|0.11%\n|-\n|62\n|[[Kulung people (Nepal)|Kulung]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|28,613\n|0.11%\n|-\n|63\n|[[Bengalis|Bengali]]\n|Other\n|26,582\n|0.10%\n|-\n|64\n|Gaderi/Bhediyar\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|26,375\n|0.10%\n|-\n|65\n|[[Dhimal]]\n|Adivasi-Tarai\n|26,298\n|0.10%\n|-\n|66\n|[[Yakkha]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|24,336\n|0.10%\n|-\n|67\n|Ghale\n|Janajati-Hill\n|22,881\n|0.09%\n|-\n|68\n|Tajpuriya\n|Adivasi-Tarai\n|19,213\n|0.07%\n|-\n|69\n|Khawas\n|Janajati-Hill\n|18,513\n|0.07%\n|-\n|70\n|Darai\n|Janajati-Hill\n|16,789\n|0.06%\n|-\n|71\n|[[Mali caste|Mali]]\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|14,995\n|0.06%\n|-\n|72\n|Dhuniya\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|14,846\n|0.06%\n|-\n|73\n|Pahari\n|Janajati-Hill\n|13,615\n|0.05%\n|-\n|74\n|[[Rajdhoves|Rajdhob]]\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|13,422\n|0.05%\n|-\n|75\n|[[Bhotiya|Bhote]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|13,397\n|0.05%\n|-\n|76\n|[[Dom (caste)|Dom]]\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|13,268\n|0.05%\n|-\n|77\n|[[Thakali people|Thakali]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|13,215\n|0.05%\n|-\n|78\n|[[Kori caste|Kori]]\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|12,276\n|0.05%\n|-\n|79\n|[[Chhantyal]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|11,810\n|0.04%\n|-\n|80\n|[[Hyolmo people|Hyolmo]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|10,752\n|0.04%\n|-\n|81\n|Bote\n|Janajati-Hill\n|10,397\n|0.04%\n|-\n|82\n|[[Rajbhar]]\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|9,542\n|0.04%\n|-\n|83\n|Brahmu/Baramo\n|Janajati-Hill\n|8,140\n|0.03%\n|-\n|84\n|[[Punjabis|Punjabi]]\n|Other\n|7,176\n|0.03%\n|-\n|85\n|Nachhring\n|Janajati-Hill\n|7,154\n|0.03%\n|-\n|86\n|Yamphu\n|Janajati-Hill\n|6,933\n|0.03%\n|-\n|87\n|Gaine\n|Khas (Dalit)\n|6,791\n|0.03%\n|-\n|88\n|Chamling\n|Janajati-Hill\n|6,668\n|0.03%\n|-\n|89\n|Athpahariya\n|Janajati-Hill\n|5,977\n|0.02%\n|-\n|90\n|[[Jirel people|Jirel]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|5,774\n|0.02%\n|-\n|91\n|Dura\n|Janajati-Hill\n|5,394\n|0.02%\n|-\n|92\n|Sarabaria\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|4,906\n|0.02%\n|-\n|93\n|[[Mech tribe|Meche]]\n|Adivasi-Tarai\n|4,867\n|0.02%\n|-\n|94\n|Bantaba\n|Janajati-Hill\n|4,604\n|0.02%\n|-\n|95\n|[[Raji people|Raji]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|4,235\n|0.02%\n|-\n|96\n|Dolpo\