e]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|13,397\n|0.05%\n|-\n|76\n|[[Dom (caste)|Dom]]\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|13,268\n|0.05%\n|-\n|77\n|[[Thakali people|Thakali]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|13,215\n|0.05%\n|-\n|78\n|[[Kori caste|Kori]]\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|12,276\n|0.05%\n|-\n|79\n|[[Chhantyal]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|11,810\n|0.04%\n|-\n|80\n|[[Hyolmo people|Hyolmo]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|10,752\n|0.04%\n|-\n|81\n|Bote\n|Janajati-Hill\n|10,397\n|0.04%\n|-\n|82\n|[[Rajbhar]]\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|9,542\n|0.04%\n|-\n|83\n|Brahmu/Baramo\n|Janajati-Hill\n|8,140\n|0.03%\n|-\n|84\n|[[Punjabis|Punjabi]]\n|Other\n|7,176\n|0.03%\n|-\n|85\n|Nachhring\n|Janajati-Hill\n|7,154\n|0.03%\n|-\n|86\n|Yamphu\n|Janajati-Hill\n|6,933\n|0.03%\n|-\n|87\n|Gaine\n|Khas (Dalit)\n|6,791\n|0.03%\n|-\n|88\n|Chamling\n|Janajati-Hill\n|6,668\n|0.03%\n|-\n|89\n|Athpahariya\n|Janajati-Hill\n|5,977\n|0.02%\n|-\n|90\n|[[Jirel people|Jirel]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|5,774\n|0.02%\n|-\n|91\n|Dura\n|Janajati-Hill\n|5,394\n|0.02%\n|-\n|92\n|Sarabaria\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|4,906\n|0.02%\n|-\n|93\n|[[Mech tribe|Meche]]\n|Adivasi-Tarai\n|4,867\n|0.02%\n|-\n|94\n|Bantaba\n|Janajati-Hill\n|4,604\n|0.02%\n|-\n|95\n|[[Raji people|Raji]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|4,235\n|0.02%\n|-\n|96\n|Dolpo\n|Janajati-Hill\n|4,107\n|0.02%\n|-\n|97\n|Halkhor\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|4,003\n|0.02%\n|-\n|98\n|Byansi/Sauka\n|Janajati-Hill\n|3,895\n|0.01%\n|-\n|99\n|Amat\n|Madhesi (Low)\n|3,830\n|0.01%\n|-\n|100\n|Thulung\n|Janajati-Hill\n|3,535\n|0.01%\n|-\n|101\n|[[Lepcha people|Lepcha]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|3,445\n|0.01%\n|-\n|102\n|Pathakatta/Kushwadia\n|Adivasi-Tarai\n|3,182\n|0.01%\n|-\n|103\n|[[Mewahang]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|3,100\n|0.01%\n|-\n|104\n|[[Bahing]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|3,096\n|0.01%\n|-\n|105\n|Natuwa\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|3,062\n|0.01%\n|-\n|106\n|[[Hayu]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|2,925\n|0.01%\n|-\n|107\n|Dhankar/[[Dharkar|Dharikar]]\n|Madhesi (Dalit)\n|2,681\n|0.01%\n|-\n|108\n|[[Lhoba people|Lhopa]]\n|Janajati-Hill\n|2,624\n|0.01%\n|-\n|109\n|[[Munda people|Munda]]\n|Adivasi-Tarai\n|2,350